org.cougaar.util
Class Translations

java.lang.Object
  org.cougaar.util.Translations

public final class Translations
extends java.lang.Object

Translations holds a set of static methods for translating between various representations of objects, primarily collection-like things. For the most part, this functionality should either not be needed (e.g. enumeration versus iteration) or belongs in core java.
